1. move the file from one module to another module:
   cut and paste and chooose "refactor" the entire project

2. rename the file:
   find "Refactor" button in tool window, in the dropdown menu select "rename file"
   
3. replace in all files:
    Ctrl + Shift + R
    
4. review code:
   click the right-bottom "git" tab, choose the "master" branch and click the compare. We can compare it with our own local branch

5. indent/unindent
   Indent Selection (Tab)
   Unindent Selection (Shift+Tab)
